cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is about a new network architecture for volumetric segmentation using 2D convolutions and maximum intensity projections. This is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions medical imaging as an application area, which could also suggest the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM).
